      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not suitable for regular use without significant repairs. The engine requires a major overhaul due to persistent stalling and internal noise, and the transmission exhibits slipping between gears. Externally, there is noticeable rust on the quarter panels and several deep scratches, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear on the upholstery. This is a project car best suited for someone with mechanical expertise or for use as a parts donor.",
