    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It drives like a dream and is totally ready for its next big adventure! If you're looking for something dependable that still looks great on the road, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
