      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a well-sorted E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, an engine renowned for its eight individual throttle bodies and 8,400 RPM redline. This example utilizes a 6-speed manual gearbox to send power through a variable M-differential lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip and driver engagement. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and maintains its factory-spec kinematic precision. Preventative maintenance is up to date, specifically addressing the rod bearings and throttle actuators to ensure long-term valvetrain integrity. While showing minor signs of use typical for its age, the car remains a robust performer with a crisp hydraulic steering response and balanced 50/50 weight distribution.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Regularly serviced. Clean title. Everything functions as intended.",
      "price": 31500.0,
