      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a mechanically sound example of the legendary E46 platform. At its heart is the high-revving S54 straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that pulls cleanly to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag six-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring excellent power delivery out of corners. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service, preserving the structural rigidity of the chassis. The suspension geometry remains precise, offering the communicative feedback and balanced handling characteristics that define the M division's engineering peak. This is a robust, driver-spec machine primed for spirited performance.",
